HEADWORD: Ambient
<hw>Am"bi*ent</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Something that surrounds or
invests; <as>as, air . . . being a perpetual
<ex>ambient</ex></as>.</def> <rj><au>Sir H. Wotton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
